$interpreted: Bandit Goon: Hey, show me what's in your hand!
Kittyeyes: Tch...we were so close...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Damnit...
PAFF: NEKO!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Why are you here!?
PAFF: I'll explain later...I'm gonna get you two out of there right away!
Bandit Goon: In your dreams! You better...
Kittyeyes: Good job, NEKO!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Teehee, NEKO has a lot of experience. Stuff like being kidnapped is no big deal to me~
PAFF: Thank goodness...you're both safe.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You...how did you know we were here?
PAFF: A doctor told me that he saw you going in this direction.
PAFF: So I followed his directions and suddenly heard some strange music. Soon after, I saw you two being taken away...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Then why didn't you come and save NEKO!?
PAFF: Sorry, there were just too many of them...
PAFF: I had no choice but to secretly follow them here. Then, just as I was observing the terrain outside, I ran into someone by the name of Roger──
Kittyeyes: You mean brother Roger!?
Kittyeyes: So that sound outside was indeed...!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ah! Hey! Wait for NEKO!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...Hey, let's get outta here!
PAFF: O-okay!
Kittyeyes: Let go of me! Brother Roger, brother Roger!
